title: Municipality Finance issues EUR 11.5 million notes and a NOK 500 million tap under its MTN programme - Yahoo Finance

description: Municipality Finance PlcStock exchange release 31 January 2022 at 10:00 am (EET) Municipality Finance issues EUR 11.5 million notes and a NOK 500 million tap under its MTN programme On 1 February 2022 Municipality Finance Plc issues EUR 11.5 million notes and a new tranche in an amount of NOK 500 million to an existing series of notes issued on 13 January 2021.
